All Classes

  • All Classes Class Summary Enum Summary 
    Class Description
    AddressHandler
    AddressHandler is used by Preprocessor to standardize address fields.
    BlockMap
    BlockMap holds our map for Indexing the data.
    CalcPerformance
    CalcPerformance contains holds data related to accuracy and number of matches.
    CompareRecord
    CompareRecord performs our calculation of similarity (confidence).
    Contact
    Generic data holder for Contact data.
    CSVInputException  
    CSVReader
    CSVReader reads in data from CSV files and stores the records in groups.
    CSVReader.Headers
    Defines the fields in our CSV files.
    EDA  
    Group
    Data holder for similar records.
    Indexer
    Indexer phonetically encodes data, and passes the encoded data as a key to BlockMap.
    Init
    Init reads a .properties file for the project and initializes objects with the values.
    MasterContact
    MasterContact extends Contact's data storage and adds functionality to store top matches.
    Matcher
    Matcher is where everything comes together.
    MatchMain  
    MatchRunner
    MatchRunner is the main "driver" of the program.
    Performance
    Performance is where information gets printed to stdout.
    Preprocessor
    Preprocessor cleans and standardizes data as it's being read in by CSVReader.
    TopMatches
    Data storage for each MasterContact's top contacts.
    UpdateWeights  
    weightNames
    weightNames is used to define the names of weights that we expect from the weight JSON files.
    Weights
    Weights reads in the values stored in json files in ./config/weights/.
